{"tid":444694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(暗瘡jj入)有冇人知暗瘡印點去","createTime":"2017-10-22T16:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T17:18:57.000Z","uid":149773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2694ee4817e77c206af80159ad4d1eda730ee556","tid":444694,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"自問自己都算乾淨<br />\n日手都會洗面做足保養<br />\n但係啲暗瘡印同皮膚都係好易生石頭瘡<br />\n有冇手足知道有咩產品or方法去到印<br />\n同等皮膚冇咁敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到依家自己塊面咁多印真係好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdeb5d8f84c2a5cbc5bff938f0e7d6096ed88c9","tid":444694,"uid":13873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ca2b9914e8eea1d9b946db8d5c958458bc51b44b","tid":444694,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"訓前推一推"},{"pid":"9df186402a8ece19bd24777ff54fba3203c9d7db","tid":444694,"uid":146924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"石頭瘡嘅話多啲做去角質，買啲清潔泥mask吸污糟野<br />\n想暗瘡印快啲淡嘅話嘥錢買咁多護膚品其實都唔太有用，最有效嘅方法就係勤力洗面多啲去角質加快皮膚更新周期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常每28日就係皮膚一次更新周期"},{"pid":"5df28ae698c0cc5fd5c590d8bc8b2288b5f6a9ea","tid":444694,"uid":146924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"個人覺得要加蘋果醋自己撈嗰隻印度神泥吸力好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次敷完塊面好似輕左咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暗粒都少咗生<br />\n<br />\n不過一大盒每次又唔用得多所以10世都唔會用得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議搵幾個朋友夾一罐"},{"pid":"d15b499fbe6549bf7788a77b094c6544a75e66ce","tid":444694,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"